bio: A podcast and newsletter segment covering Optimism ecosystem news.
impactDescription:
ETH Daily boosts the Optimism Collective's brand awareness, reaching over 2,200 crypto enthusiasts. ETH Daily provides essential OP News coverage, keeping end-users, developers, journalists, and crypto security firms informed about network upgrades and new OP Stack chains. ETH Daily has even helped inspire news articles, like this one (bit.ly/op_inspire) published by The Block on Optimism Airdrop 3 after the journalist read the ETH Daily newsletter.

Inspire example: bit.ly/op_inspire
OP News Stats: ethdaily.io/retropgf3
contributionDescription: ETH Daily provided over 100 OP News updates to an audience of 2,200 podcast listeners and 230 newsletter subscribers. In the fast-changing Optimism Collective, ETH Daily plays a crucial role in keeping users well-informed. OP News is a series of Optimism-related updates featured in over 100 episodes in a segment called Optimism Highlights.
